        <li>Use a <code class="text-stone-900 bg-stone-200/70 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">while</code> loop to keep prompting the user until they provide valid input.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

## How to Test Your Code

Does your code work as prescribed when you input:

- `-1` (or other negative numbers)?
- `0`?
- `1` through `8`?
- `9` or other positive numbers?
- Letters or words?
- No input at all, when you only hit Enter?

